{"tid":1966082,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法搵齊美心員工","createTime":"2020-04-10T02:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T14:13:47.000Z","uid":44898,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e53b599b1b73a754ba62b3d33a4cc61cb4915026","tid":1966082,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:32:20.000Z","msg":"美心班伙記，俾黑心公司強扣有薪假<br />\n依家政府派錢都係一個月克扣2日<br />\n<br />\n有無方法集齊班苦主上奴工署<br />\n一齊投訴搞下黑心<br />\n<br />\n一個員工一年扣24日<br />\n一日600，一個食最小14400<br />\n計5000個員工，一年都執唔小"},{"pid":"73c19d97f3c558915bf57475b8f6dcf21f0b64e8","tid":1966082,"uid":44898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"有無對奴工法例熟悉睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwDpYJm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwDpYJm.jpg&h=958f988c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美心請人廣告寫6日例假<br />\n見工講明放6日<br />\n而張約條款就如圖中<br />\n<br />\n美心大石責死蟹<br />\n單方面就改成4日<br />\n逼員工簽張野<br />\n有無得上奴工署嘈佢呢"},{"pid":"a47daf82e953f63af63dcbb8670d821f43640933","tid":1966082,"uid":44898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"今日見立場新聞講依單野<br />\n<br />\n美心同好多大集團一樣<br />\n份實際人工係使用津貼，<br />\n勤工，假期<br />\n拉高個平均價到市場合理水位<br />\n你俾佢食2日，等同減薪1000以上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一年食你最小12000<br />\n變相食左2 年人工加幅"},{"pid":"15114d32f12dd8e0922c8867b834f1da353719a3","tid":1966082,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27d90194142e33c6beff1038342cdd3592714356","tid":1966082,"uid":40902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T11:40:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0bed0c371364484621cf539b67c9d72d8b3af64","tid":1966082,"uid":189099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"美心工真係比狗做<br />\n<br />\n利申 以前做過"}]}